node.text:
I remember briefing Chef about our vision to marry Chocolate & Ghee; I will never forget the expression on his face!

Until today, i have been unable to decipher if he thought “Wow, that's amazing!" OR "Okay, this is going to be really difficult!". 

In the meanwhile, here's a small snippet of what the journey looked like in creating the @epigamia.official Ghee Spreads!

Link in bio

“I have always admired my mother’s style. For as long as I can remember, her style has been classic, elegant and something I have related to.” Actor Deepika Padukone (@deepikapadukone) is the new face to be affiliated with Chopard’s (@chopard) ‘Happy Diamonds’ collection. Read more about her association with Chopard, what according to her makes watches and jewellery stand the test of time, and how the actor finds her happy place, in the link in bio.

On Deepika: ‘Happy Sport’ watch in stainless steel and 18K ethical rose gold with a 33mm dial featuring dancing diamonds by Chopard
